title: Hour 1: First Take in Frisco
description:
First Take travels to Frisco, Texas for a show in front of a Cowboy crowd. Michael Irvin and Dez Bryant join the show. The crew discusses CeeDee Lamb, Tyron Smith's injury, and where Dallas ranks in the NFC.
